  VARIABLE:
          Names are AID FAM sex age_1 age_3
          white african native asian other hispanic
          income par_ed
          PC34A PC34B PC34C PC34D PC34E PC44A
          H1WP9 H1WP10 H1PF1 H1PF2 H1PF3 H1PF4 H1PF5
          H1WP13 H1WP14 H1PF23 H1PF24 H1PF25
